<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Moderator Application Result - Not Approved</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333; /* --text-color-dark approximation */
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f0f8ff; /* --bg-main */
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #ccebff; /* Lighter shade derived from --border-color */
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ccebff;
      }
      .header h2 {
        color: #003666; /* --bg-dark */
        margin: 0;
      }
      .content {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280; /* --muted-foreground approximation */
      }
      .reason {
        background-color: #fee2e2; /* Light red background */
        padding: 15px;
        border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; /* --destructive approximation */
        margin: 20px 0;
        color: #b91c1c; /* Darker red text */
      }
      .reason p {
        margin: 0;
      }
      .reason strong {
        color: #991b1b; /* Even darker red for emphasis */
      }
      ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      li {
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }
      a {
        color: #003666; /* --bg-dark */
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>Moderator Application Result</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear Applicant,</p>

        <p>
          Thank you for your interest in becoming a moderator for UniNav. After
          careful review of your application, we regret to inform you that we
          are unable to approve your request at this time.
        </p>

        <div class="reason">
          <p><strong>Reason:</strong></p>
          <p><%= comment %></p>
        </div>

        <p>
          While we cannot proceed with your application at this moment, we
          encourage you to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Continue being an active member of our community.</li>
          <li>
            Consider applying again after addressing the mentioned concerns.
          </li>
          <li>Reach out to our support team if you need any clarification.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          We appreciate your understanding and your commitment to our academic
          community.
        </p>
        <p>Best regards,<br />The UniNav Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> UniNav. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
          Need help? Contact us at
          <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color: #003666"
            ><%= supportEmail %></a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
